WINDOWS:

install python 2.7
click on epimorphism.py or run with python 2.7 via a console

to take screenshots & onscreen text, install PIL(optional)


LINUX:

Dependencies - python2.7, freeglut, PIL(optional)

./epimorphism

optional: PIL, twisted

OSX:

borken


IF THE APPLICATION RUNS SLOWLY:
  try each of(default is 1536):
  ./epimorphism kernel_dim=1024
  ./epimorphism kernel_dim=512
  ./epimorphism kernel_dim=256

  until you get acceptable performance